{"tid":2312702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Apple 為2019 年 11 月至 2020 年 5 月間製造 iPhone 11，提供免費更換","createTime":"2020-12-05T07:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T16:02:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd500847d19bc3ce2a2aab266769d7b81a9df47","tid":2312702,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"如果你手上的 iPhone 11 螢幕出現觸控不靈的話，記得去查一下它的生產日期，因為 Apple 現在確定會為部分符合條件的裝置提供免費更換了。按照他們的說法，有「少部分」的 iPhone 11 螢幕「因為顯示器模組的問題」，可能造成螢幕無法回應觸控動作。受影響的手機是在 2019 年 11 月至 2020 年 5 月間製造，用戶去官網（香港 / 台灣）遞交產品序號確認資格後，便可找 Apple 進行換機了。<br />\n<br />\n需要注意的是，Apple 這項換機方案僅適用於部分 iPhone 11，iPhone 11 和 11 Pro Max 並不在更換範圍之內。若是你在使用 iPhone 11 時有遇到觸控方面困擾的話，不妨趁此機會看看有沒有可能把問題解決吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/apple-%E5%B0%87%E7%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%A7%B8%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E9%9D%88%E7%9A%84-iphone-11-%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E6%9B%B4%E6%8F%9B-054802864.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fapple-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%259D%2588%25E7%259A%2584-iphone-11-%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%258F%259B-054802864.html&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=ec143417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/apple-%E5%B0%87%E7%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%A7%B8%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E9%9D%88%E7%9A%84-iphone-11-%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E6%9B%B4%E6%8F%9B-054802864.html</a>"},{"pid":"cad0e813f091b027e8a593bdd1c659f700c2b5b7","tid":2312702,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:36:31.000Z","msg":"HK?"},{"pid":"b75f1c94b8db7b49903c278f17cd7cd0bbd49d0c","tid":2312702,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:37:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/iphone-11-display-modul